It's a pity Ji Bozai destroyed
the Golden Millet Dream.

00:02:56.065 --> 00:02:57.225
Otherwise…

00:02:57.305 --> 00:02:59.625
It's not over yet.

00:02:59.705 --> 00:03:02.385
Though the Diwu tree's
core hasn't been seen for ages,

00:03:02.465 --> 00:03:04.225
the Bo clan still managed to make

00:03:04.305 --> 00:03:06.505
the Golden Millet Dream and
the Heavenly Grief a century ago.

00:03:06.585 --> 00:03:09.305
Since the Golden Millet Dream Ji Bozai had
was made by Fairy Bo Yulan,

00:03:09.385 --> 00:03:11.025
