00:03:11.985 --> 00:03:13.825
That's my disciple. Smart as ever.

00:03:13.905 --> 00:03:15.705
If they could find it, why can't we?

00:03:16.705 --> 00:03:18.825
What matters most is the Diwu tree's core.

00:03:18.905 --> 00:03:21.985
The rest of the ingredients,
like Ostrich Rat, mesona,

00:03:22.065 --> 00:03:23.305
and turtle shells,

00:03:23.385 --> 00:03:24.225
are easy to get.

00:03:25.545 --> 00:03:27.385
Ming Yi, don't worry.

00:03:27.465 --> 00:03:30.345
-With me here, there's nothing to fear.
-I know.

00:03:30.425 --> 00:03:31.385
When you're here, Master,

00:03:31.465 --> 00:03:33.265
I feel safer
than when my father was around.

00:03:39.545 --> 00:03:40.585
What's wrong?

00:03:44.825 --> 00:03:46.985
You're getting more sentimental

00:03:47.065 --> 00:03:49.105
with age, aren't you?

00:03:49.185 --> 00:03:51.465
If you want to cry, go ahead.
Here, my shoulder's free.

00:03:54.345 --> 00:03:56.265
What are you doing? I'm your master.

00:03:56.345 --> 00:03:57.505
Show some respect.

00:03:59.105 --> 00:04:02.545
