make the Golden Millet Dream,

00:04:02.625 --> 00:04:04.545
I'll not only reenter
the Qingyun Tournament,

00:04:04.625 --> 00:04:06.345
but I'll also win
it for another seven years.

00:04:08.985 --> 00:04:11.505
Is this the time
to be thinking about that?

00:04:14.585 --> 00:04:15.745
But you're right.

00:04:16.425 --> 00:04:17.345
No matter how hard it is,

00:04:18.585 --> 00:04:19.785
we'll find those ingredients.

00:04:21.184 --> 00:04:24.825
I can't stand
watching you suffer any longer.

00:04:30.465 --> 00:04:31.905
Show some respect.

00:04:33.025 --> 00:04:34.385
You cheeky brat.

00:04:39.225 --> 00:04:41.905
The last ingredient for the Golden
Millet Dream is the Diwu tree's core?

00:04:43.385 --> 00:04:44.665
How could we possibly find that?

00:04:45.385 --> 00:04:47.265
The Diwu tree's core
has vanished from the world,

00:04:49.025 --> 00:04:50.985
but I can't just watch her die.

00:04:52.905 --> 00:04:53.945
Fuyue,

00:04:54.465 --> 00:04:57.385
the Yousu Fox Tribe can seal a primordial
spirit within an Illusory Realm,

00:04:58.545 --> 00:05:00.705
which is considered a form of immortality.

00:05:01.825 --> 00:05:02.905
So I wonder,

00:05:03.905 --> 00:05:04.985
could this technique

00:05:06.105 --> 00:05:07.945
be used to keep Ming Yi alive for now?

00:05:10.625 --> 00:05:11.985
Have you lost your mind, Your Lordship?

00:05:12.905 --> 00:05:14.105
You know full well

00:05:14.185 --> 00:05:16.705
that using the technique like that

00:05:16.785 --> 00:05:20.265
inflicts burning pain to the bone.
One mistake,

00:05:20.785 --> 00:05:23.865
and you'll lose your mind completely!

00:05:23.945 --> 00:05:25.785
You're only talking
about the consequences.

00:05:27.065 --> 00:05:28.505
That means

00:05:29.985 --> 00:05:31.825
the method itself can work.

00:05:32.345 --> 00:05:33.625
Am I right?

00:05:42.865 --> 00:05:44.065
-Please…
-Your Lordship!

00:05:50.145 --> 00:05:51.505
Please.

00:05:54.705 --> 00:05:55.945
I'm begging you.

00:05:57.585 --> 00:05:58.705
Your Lordship.

00:06:07.145 --> 00:06:10.385
This fox spell can lure
souls into an Illusory Realm.

00:06:10.905 --> 00:06:13.745
It can strip a being of
their three souls and seven senses

00:06:13.825 --> 00:06:15.105
and weave an Illusory Realm.

00:06:15.865 --> 00:06:18.265
Within that Illusory Realm,
the spell can be reversed

00:06:18.785 --> 00:06:22.385
to extend her life with
someone else's lifespan.

00:06:22.465 --> 00:06:25.105
I can capture some
wandering spirits without families.

00:06:25.185 --> 00:06:27.785
They have no ties in this world.

00:06:27.865 --> 00:06:31.065
Killing them won't cause any trouble.

00:06:31.145 --> 00:06:32.425
We can't do that.

00:06:32.505 --> 00:06:35.585
If I stain my hands
with the blood of the innocent,

00:06:35.665 --> 00:06:37.665
Ming Yi will never forgive me,

00:06:37.745 --> 00:06:39.625
and I'll lose any
chance of a future with her.

00:06:39.705 --> 00:06:40.745
Even now,

00:06:41.385 --> 00:06:43.065
Your Lordship still can't bring yourself

00:06:43.145 --> 00:06:45.105
to lie to her?

00:06:45.185 --> 00:06:46.745
This is my only wish.

00:06:47.625 --> 00:06:48.785
I have deceived her before

00:06:49.425 --> 00:06:51.385
and done many things I can never undo.

00:06:51.905 --> 00:06:52.905
But in the end,

00:06:53.705 --> 00:06:55.665
I must become someone like her

00:06:56.265 --> 00:06:58.505
to be worthy of standing by her side.

00:07:45.105 --> 00:07:49.585
Three souls and seven
senses, enter the endless Illusory Realm.

00:07:50.585 --> 00:07:56.105
Burn the heart and refine the blood.
Cross the heavens and the netherworld.

00:07:56.185 --> 00:07:58.225
With my bare body and organs,

00:07:58.825 --> 00:08:00.225
I offer all my life's fortune

00:08:01.225 --> 00:08:02.825
to lengthen her years

00:08:03.345 --> 00:08:04.865
and extend her life.

00:08:20.545 --> 00:08:22.305
-Ming Yi!
-Immortal Situ.

00:08:23.105 --> 00:08:24.825
I found a way to save you.

00:08:24.905 --> 00:08:25.985
Take this medicine.

00:08:26.585 --> 00:08:27.425
What is it?

00:08:27.505 --> 00:08:29.225
Ming Yi, just take it.

00:08:29.305 --> 00:08:30.785
Tell me what it is.

00:08:42.065 --> 00:08:45.625
I learned a technique
that refines the blood of my heart.

00:08:45.705 --> 00:08:47.185
This way,

00:08:47.865 --> 00:08:50.865
I can trade my lifespan for your time.

00:08:52.225 --> 00:08:54.825
Ming Yi, I told you,

00:08:55.465 --> 00:08:57.025
I won't let you die.

00:09:02.425 --> 00:09:03.265
Ming Yi.

00:09:09.705 --> 00:09:10.745
You…

00:09:12.625 --> 00:09:14.225
Immortal Situ!

00:09:15.905 --> 00:09:16.825
You…

00:09:58.825 --> 00:09:59.865
You're awake.

00:10:00.385 --> 00:10:01.465
How do you feel?

00:10:02.545 --> 00:10:03.505
Have some water.

00:10:11.905 --> 00:10:12.745
Here.

00:10:25.665 --> 00:10:28.145
Ming Yi, you know

00:10:29.265 --> 00:10:30.505
I did this willingly.

00:10:32.025 --> 00:10:33.225
Immortal Situ,

00:10:34.265 --> 00:10:35.985
when I took you to
the Qingyun Tournament years ago,

00:10:36.065 --> 00:10:37.025
it was just a small favor.

00:10:38.225 --> 00:10:40.585
Why are you so fixated on it

00:10:41.305 --> 00:10:42.825
that you went this far for me?

00:10:46.065 --> 00:10:46.905
Ming Yi,

00:10:48.105 --> 00:10:49.625
this is the first time

00:10:50.185 --> 00:10:51.865
you've acknowledged
who you truly are to me.

00:10:54.705 --> 00:10:56.225
I always knew,

00:10:58.105 --> 00:10:59.705
but hearing you admit it yourself

00:11:00.825 --> 00:11:01.985
means so much more.

00:11:04.545 --> 00:11:05.665
I'm sorry.

00:11:05.745 --> 00:11:08.865
You see me as your sister,
yet I kept secrets from you.

00:11:10.345 --> 00:11:12.225
You've held no grudge

00:11:12.305 --> 00:11:14.025
and helped me again and again.

00:11:14.105 --> 00:11:15.345
I truly don't know how to repay you.

00:11:20.905 --> 00:11:21.825
In fact, I was already

00:11:24.425 --> 00:11:26.425
in deep despair back then.

00:11:28.425 --> 00:11:31.105
If you hadn't taken me
to that Qingyun Tournament,

00:11:32.625 --> 00:11:34.825
stood on the Totem Platform with my badge,

00:11:34.905 --> 00:11:36.945
and said those words to me,

00:11:38.785 --> 00:11:40.225
I don't think I could've kept going.

00:11:43.825 --> 00:11:44.665
So,

00:11:46.465 --> 00:11:48.265
no matter how much lifespan it costs,

00:11:49.945 --> 00:11:51.665
I'm willing to give it.

00:11:52.905 --> 00:11:54.065
Ming Yi,

00:11:54.585 --> 00:11:55.825
without you,

00:11:56.665 --> 00:11:58.745
I would've given up on my life long ago.

00:11:59.985 --> 00:12:01.025
So,

00:12:03.225 --> 00:12:05.185
think of this as me fulfilling my wish.

00:12:09.065 --> 00:12:10.225
This time,

00:12:12.145 --> 00:12:13.985
let me be the one to keep you alive.

00:12:19.705 --> 00:12:21.705
You can't make
someone else your purpose in life.

00:12:21.785 --> 00:12:23.185
You should live for yourself.

00:12:25.985 --> 00:12:27.105
Immortal Situ,

00:12:27.185 --> 00:12:29.025
in truth, I'm the one who owes you.

00:12:29.105 --> 00:12:30.585
In that case,

00:12:31.225 --> 00:12:32.665
promise me one thing.

00:12:36.505 --> 00:12:37.905
I haven't decided what it will be yet,

00:12:39.625 --> 00:12:41.265
but you'll do

00:12:43.145 --> 00:12:44.505
whatever I ask for me,

00:12:46.065 --> 00:12:46.985
won't you?

00:13:34.025 --> 00:13:34.865
Your Lordship!

00:13:37.065 --> 00:13:37.985
Your Lordship.

00:13:47.425 --> 00:13:48.265
Your Lordship,

00:13:48.945 --> 00:13:50.945
you're suffering
the aftereffects of reversing the spell.

00:13:51.025 --> 00:13:53.865
If you give in,
you'll lose your mind completely.

00:13:53.945 --> 00:13:54.785
Hang in there.

00:13:59.505 --> 00:14:00.985
Fox blood can ease the pain for now.

00:14:02.025 --> 00:14:02.905
Your Lordship.

00:14:20.305 --> 00:14:21.225
Your Lordship.

00:14:37.025 --> 00:14:38.225
It doesn't hurt.

00:14:44.665 --> 00:14:46.545
Old Man She! Old Man She!

00:14:46.625 --> 00:14:47.545
Look! They're back!

00:14:47.625 --> 00:14:50.345
Just now, they suddenly recovered!

00:14:50.425 --> 00:14:52.545
-What did you say?
-My spiritual veins! Look!

00:15:07.505 --> 00:15:08.345
All right.

00:15:08.425 --> 00:15:11.425
-Stop using your spiritual power.
-No, look. They're really back. Look.

00:15:16.185 --> 00:15:18.385
And the Grief Blossom
isn't showing itself.

00:15:22.945 --> 00:15:24.945
You're better.

00:15:25.865 --> 00:15:26.705
You've really recovered.

00:15:27.585 --> 00:15:29.825
I knew you wouldn't die!

00:15:29.905 --> 00:15:32.345
I was so worried!

00:15:35.185 --> 00:15:37.145
All right.

00:15:37.225 --> 00:15:39.545
This is good news. Why are you crying?

00:15:46.225 --> 00:15:47.465
Did it just ring?

00:15:47.545 --> 00:15:48.785
Your spiritual veins have recovered.

00:15:48.865 --> 00:15:51.145
Of course Twenty-Seven would sense it.

00:15:51.225 --> 00:15:52.945
Your companion beast will return soon.

00:15:54.105 --> 00:15:56.625
A companion beast
comes into being when a cultivator

00:15:56.705 --> 00:15:57.905
reaches the Transcendent Stage.

00:15:57.985 --> 00:15:59.305
With your spiritual veins restored,

00:16:00.025 --> 00:16:01.785
Twenty-Seven's
lingering divine consciousness

00:16:01.865 --> 00:16:02.745
will also grow stronger gradually.

00:16:02.825 --> 00:16:04.785
Soon, you'll be able to bring him back.

00:16:08.505 --> 00:16:09.385
Twenty-Seven.

00:16:12.625 --> 00:16:15.745
You said Immortal Situ
refined his heart's blood

00:16:15.825 --> 00:16:17.905
and traded his lifespan for yours?

00:16:19.745 --> 00:16:22.305
He said it was
a secret technique of his clan.

00:16:22.385 --> 00:16:24.145
I never knew

00:16:24.225 --> 00:16:26.825
that Zhushui Spiritual State
had such a powerful clan

00:16:26.905 --> 00:16:28.545
with mastery of such a rare art.

00:16:28.625 --> 00:16:31.185
